name: Rocket Mayhem (FALKon2246)
description:
This game was created using python's Pygame module

Game:

You are a spaceship who's controls are off, and your goal is to help the pilot navigate to the orb at the end of the level

Note: You cannot touch the obstacles, nor can the spaceship touch your mouse

Happy flying!

Source code: https://github.com/ill3ageef/Rocket-Mayhem
